    "description": "<p data-block-key=\"ok1k7\"><i>Biology</i> is designed to cover the scope and sequence requirements of a typical two-semester biology course for science majors. The text provides comprehensive coverage of foundational research and core biology concepts through an evolutionary lens. <i>Biology</i> includes rich features that engage students in scientific inquiry, highlight careers in the biological sciences, and offer everyday applications. The book also includes clicker questions to help students understand—and apply—key concepts.<br/><br/> This book has been superseded by <a href=\"https://openstax.org/details/books/biology-2e\">Biology 2e</a> and is no longer being updated. We recommend that you use Biology 2e, available <a href=\"https://openstax.org/books/biology/pages/1-introduction\">here</a>.</p>",
